Welcome to the Winter 2026 term of ACIT 4850 - Enterprise Systems Integration. In this course we will be installing, configuring and integrating the tools that are used by software development teams for building software applications.

We have setup a Discord server that may be used for questions and help outside of class time.

https://discord.gg/WUTeX6MfUW

