The first classes are on Tuesday, Jan. 6th for Sets B and C and Wednesday, Jan. 7th for Set A.

If you have any questions, contact Johnny (johnny_zhang@bcit.ca) for Set A or Mike on Discord or by e-mail (mmulder10@bcit.ca) for Sets B and C.

See you in class.

